item.description:
"Accomplish and be more!" That's the motto of Cashmere Coaching, run by Aimee Yawnick, a very accomplished woman herself. Aimee started in fitness training, and very successfully moved into sales and management.

Applying the same dedication and philosophy learned from these experiences, Aimee helps women accelerate their personal growth and development to maximize success in both their personal and professional lives.

If you are ready to make your SELF a priority, join us for valuable information and easy to use tools!

As usual, we'll have a raffle, so bring business cards. Look forward to seeing you there!

Cheers, Karen
617-650-8716
